'''''America – The Freedom to Be''''' was a thirteen-part German educational television series teaching the [[English language]] with an [[United States|American]] and [[Canada|Canadian]] theme. Produced by [[Westdeutscher Rundfunk|WDR]], the program is an extension of its ''[[Fast Track English]]'' series.
