'''Chak Alampur''' is a town in [[Budge Budge II]] CD Block of [[South 24 Parganas]] district in the [[India]]n [[States and territories of India|State]] of [[West Bengal]]. [[Budge Budge]] police station serves this town.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indikosh.com/vill/351945/chak-alampur|title=Primary Census Abstract Data of Chak Alampur|work=Census of India|publisher=Indikosh|accessdate=26 April 2016}}</ref>
==Geography== Chak Alampur town is located at {{coord|22.4161|N|88.1655|E|format=dms}}. It has an average elevation of {{convert|9|m}}.
